Blender is a professional free and open-source 3D computer graphics software.

== Installation ==
Installation of Blender on Gentoo is rather complicated. Described setup works for version 2.72b, may quickly become obsolete.
* unmask python 3.4 use flags:
{{RootCmd|cat /etc/portage/profile/use.stable.mask|output=<pre>
-python_targets_python3_4
-python_single_target_python3_4</pre>}}
* use eapi 5
{{RootCmd|cat /etc/portage/profile/eapi|output=<pre>5</pre>}}
* setup blender use flags
{{RootCmd|grep blender /etc/portage/package.use|output=
<pre>media-gfx/blender python_targets_python3_4 python_single_target_python3_4 cycles openimageio player fftw openal</pre>}}
Use flags {{UseFlag|package=media-gfx/blender
|python_targets_python3_4
|python_single_target_python3_4
|cycles
|player
|fftw
|openal}}
